second, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEaAy^imu","text_ar":"دَعَايِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (of the last, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diEamN","text_ar":"دِعَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqaAmN fulaAnN daEaAy^ima AlA_isolaAmi","text_ar":"اَقَامٌ فُلَانٌ دَعَايِمَ الاـِسْلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one set up the supports of El-Islám"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA mino daEaAy^imi AlA^umuwri","text_ar":"هٰذَا مِنْ دَعَايِمِ الاُمُورِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is of the things whereby affairs are held together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diEaAmapN","text_ar":"دِعَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa diEaAmapu Alqawomi","text_ar":"هُوَ دِعَامَةُ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the lord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief, of the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their support,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stay;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) like as one says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa diEaAmuhumo","text_ar":"هُوَ دِعَامُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo daEaAy^imu","text_ar":"هُمْ دَعَايِمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomihimo","text_ar":"قَوْمِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are the lords,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chiefs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the supports,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stays, of their people"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) 'Omar Ibn-El-Khattáb was called by 'Omar Ibn-'AbdEl-'Azeez"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diEaAmapu AlD~aEiyfi","text_ar":"دِعَامَةُ الضَّعِيفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The support,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stay, of the weak"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  Also, (K,) or [correctly]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diEaAmataAni","text_ar":"دِعَامَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diEomataAni","text_ar":"دِعْمَتَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upright"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of wood of the pulley"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that support the cross piece to which the pulley is suspended"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K, TA:) such as are made of clay are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuronuwqaAni","text_ar":"زُرْنُوقَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","AHn"]}]}}